text:
I don't know why it took me so FRIKKIN long to try this place. My boyfriend took me, for my first time. I was a bit sus, to be honest. Because a lot of the other places like this, in town, are pretty much ... trash. I was SO blown away with Island Flavor.

All I gotta say is;

I now need furikake chicken from here, at least once or twice a week. :-) The portion is so perfect too.
